PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Common Questions About Our Ethereum Transaction Finder
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app allows you to quickly find and explore new transactions on the Ethereum blockchain in real-time. Stay up-to-date on the latest activity.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We connect directly to Ethereum nodes to stream incoming transactions as they get mined into new blocks. Our algorithms filter and sort the transactions based on customizable criteria.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What can I use it for?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Track transactions to/from specific wallet addresses, monitor high-value transfers, explore smart contract interactions, and more. Useful for analysis, auditing, and dApp building.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Do I need an Ethereum node?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: No, our service handles all the node operation and synchronization for you. Just provide your preferences and API key to start streaming transactions.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our app for tracking new Ethereum transactions.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app allows you to monitor the Ethereum blockchain in real-time and get notified of new transactions as they occur. Perfect for traders, analysts, and developers.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We connect directly to Ethereum nodes and stream new block and transaction data. Using our filtering tools, you can customize which transactions trigger alerts based on criteria like value, addresses, and more.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Do I need any special software?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: No, our app runs in your web browser - no installation required. We also offer API access for programmatic integration.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: New transactions are typically visible in our app within seconds after being included in a new Ethereum block. Our infrastructure is highly optimized for speed.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: We offer a free tier for basic usage and paid subscriptions with more advanced filtering, higher data limits, and enhanced performance. Check our pricing page for the latest plans.
